data.description: This exquisite 3-bedroom townhome features 1 1/2 baths, a 2-car garage, and a spacious open floor plan combining the living and dining areas. The unit includes convenient in-unit laundry, and all appliances are included. Step out onto your private balcony through the sliders. The lower level, designed as an English basement, offers a family room or a potential 4th bedroom. Recently painted, new furnace. Located near Route 120 and Route 12, this home is close to restaurants, shopping centers, and a neighborhood park with scenic walking trails around a pond. Truly, this is an exceptionally wonderful place to live.
